Things I did in this game:

* explored underworld;
* discovered amazing spells;
* died, very often;
* angered gods;
* fought bosses;
* defeated my CPU and GPU at the same time;
* ate hallucinogenic mushrooms;
* blew 500 nuclear bombs per second;
* made gods afraid of me.

10/10, this game is one of a kind.

P.S. if your FPS doesn't drop when you cast a spell in this game, you're probably not strong enough yet.

